## Artifact Checklist (Where to Find Everything)

### Documentation Folder
- Revised SRS (PDF + source): `documentation/`
  - PDF: `documentation/SRS.pdf` (or your exact filename)
  - Source: `documentation/SRS.docx` (or your exact filename)
- Updated Gantt chart (planned vs actual): `documentation/`
  - `documentation/gantt.pdf` (or your exact filename)

### Source Code Folder
- Application source code: `src/`
  - Next.js app routes: `src/app/`
  - Reusable components: `src/app/components/` and/or `src/components/`
  - Supabase helpers: `src/lib/`

### Deployment & Setup Folder
- Install + setup instructions: `deployment/INSTALL.md`

### User Documentation Folder
- User guide + screenshots: `user-docs/USER_GUIDE.md`
- Screenshots: `user-docs/screenshots/`